                    you are already familiar with. Start working effectively from day one.</p>
                <div class="benefits-testimonial">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="small-2 columns">
                            <img src="<%= img_path %>template/ModCustomers/nuxeo/nuxeo-avatar.png">
                        </div>
                        <div class="small-10 columns">
                            <p>„Handsontable had the greatest documentation, and an impressive feature set”</p>
                            <p>Alain Escaffre, VP at Nuxeo</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center artwork">
                <svg class="svg">
                    <use xlink:href="#spreadsheet-experience"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-6 columns text-center artwork">
                <svg class="svg">
                    <use xlink:href="#powerful-features"></use>
                </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <h2>
                    <hr/>
                    Created for developers
                </h2>
                <p>Handsontable is aimed to be as easy to implement and customize as possible.
                    It comes with a comprehensive API, useful tutorials and a both community and
                    commercial support.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
                <h2>
                    <hr/>
                    High performance
                </h2>
                <p>You can finally work with thousands of your data without worrying about the
